{"about_the_game":"Pathogen is a real-time strategy game, where you take control of a plague that is causing a pandemic. Your goal is to defeat humanity by improving your abilities and earning points from infections.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1907290/extras/realLifePathogens.png?t=1658417160\" /><br><br>Choose from many different types of pathogens, each with unique abilities. You can customize your plague by choosing a color and a disease name. Lots of extra customization will come in the future.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong><u>Bacteria</u></strong>: Simplicity to use. High climate resistances. Can grow a flagellum which makes it faster.<br></li><li><strong><u>Virus</u></strong>: Fast spreading speed, mutates in new strains with random benefits. However, dies fast outside of the host.<br></li><li><strong><u>Parasite</u></strong>: Play alongside mosquitoes to reach its full potential.</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1907290/extras/superplagues.png?t=1658417160\" /><br><br>Superplagues are special plagues that differ from realistic ones, as their special abilities (thankfully) are purely fictional.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong><u>Thanatus</u></strong>: Create fake outbreaks around the world, created by only collective paranoia. However, these outbreaks may be even more destructive than real ones.<br></li><li><strong><u>Radion</u></strong>: The most unstable pathogen, as radioactive material is stored in its nucleus.</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1907290/extras/lanMultiplayer.png?t=1658417160\" /><br><br>You can play PvP human vs plague games on a LAN network. In multiplayer games, you can play as the human side, placing hospitals, setting lockdowns, and researching for new medicaments, trying to stop the disease as much a